  "prompt": "What is a suitable inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Treutlen County GA?",
  "response": "There are several inpatient drug and alcohol rehab centers near Treutlen County, GA. Here are a few options:\n\n1. **Willingway** (located in Statesboro, GA)\n   - Specializes in addiction treatment.\n   - Offers various programs including detox, residential inpatient, and long-term treatment.\n\n2. **Fairview Park Hospital Behavioral Health Services** (located in Dublin, GA)\n   - Provides inpatient treatment for substance abuse.\n   - Offers comprehensive services including medical detoxification and rehabilitation.\n\n3. **Georgia Pines** (located in Thomasville, GA)\n   - Offers a range of services including inpatient treatment, outpatient care, and crisis stabilization.\n   - Focuses on mental health and substance abuse.\n\n4. **Twin Lakes Recovery Center** (located in Monroe, GA)\n   - Provides a range of services including detox, inpatient treatment, and outpatient services.\n   - Tailors treatment plans to individual needs.\n\nIt's important to research each facility to ensure it meets the specific needs of the individual seeking treatment. Checking their accreditations, reviews, and visiting the centers if possible can also provide additional insights into their suitability. Always consult with a healthcare professional for recommendations tailored to the specific situation.",
